OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FBritain's commandos will be able to
OL,8,Fboard and halt Russia's shadow fleet
OL,9,Fvessels as they pass through UK
OL,10,Fwaters, the Prime Minister has
OL,11,Fannounced.
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer said the UK would
OL,14,Fjoin northern European allies in
OL,15,Fintercepting the tankers, in an
OL,16,Fattempt to "go after" the sanction-
OL,17,Fbreaking ships "even harder".
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@UO]yD@POUyD@\O]
