PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FThe Prime Minister has given approval
OL,8,Ffor the UK to start seizing shadow
OL,9,Ffleet vessels as he travels to
OL,10,FHelsinki, Finland, for a summit with
OL,11,Fnational leaders from the Joint
OL,12,FExpeditionary Force (JEF).
OL,14,FJoint Expeditionary Force nations
OL,16,FThe JEF, a military coalition of 10
OL,17,Fnorthern European countries led by the
OL,18,FUK, aims to defend against Russian
OL,19,Fincursions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FIt also includes Denmark, Estonia,
OL,8,FFinland, Iceland, Latvia, Lithuania,
OL,9,Fthe Netherlands, Norway and Sweden.
OL,11,FMoscow's shadow fleet is reported to
OL,12,Fbe made up of more than a thousand
OL,13,Fageing tankers.
OL,15,FThey illicitly ship oil and other
OL,16,Fgoods out of Russia by flying the
OL,17,Fflags of other countries, with the aim
OL,18,Fof evading sanctions imposed by the
OL,19,FWest since the invasion of Ukraine
OL,20,Fbegan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FJEF countries Finland, Sweden and
OL,8,FEstonia have recently intercepted
OL,9,Fsuspected shadow tankers travelling
OL,10,Fthrough the Baltic.
OL,12,FClosing off British waters to the
OL,13,Fshadow fleet is aimed at forcing the
OL,14,FRussian vessels into taking longer,
OL,15,Fmore costly sea routes, or risk being
OL,16,Fintercepted by the UK.
OL,18,FSir Keir said: "We are living in an
OL,19,Fincreasingly volatile and dangerous
OL,20,Fworld, facing threats from different
OL,21,Ffronts across the world every day.
OL,26,@zD@POU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
