OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,F"As Prime Minister, my first duty is
OL,8,Fto keep this country safe and protect
OL,9,FBritish interests here and abroad.
OL,11,F"(Russian President Vladimir) Putin is
OL,12,Frubbing his hands at the war in the
OL,13,FMiddle East because he thinks higher
OL,14,Foil prices will let him line his
OL,15,Fpockets.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,F"That's why we're going after his
OL,8,Fshadow fleet even harder, not just
OL,9,Fkeeping Britain safe but starving
OL,10,FPutin's war machine of the dirty
OL,11,Fprofits that fund his barbaric
OL,12,Fcampaign in Ukraine.
OL,14,F"He and his cronies should be in no
OL,15,Fdoubt, we will always defend our
OL,16,Fsovereignty and stand with Ukraine for
OL,17,Fas long as it takes."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUyD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
