FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FBritish forces have already been
OL,8,Finvolved in tracking shadow fleet
OL,9,Fvessels for several years, and have
OL,10,Fsupported operations by other
OL,11,Fcountries to seize the ships.
OL,13,FIn January, the UK assisted in the
OL,14,Fseizure of the oil tanker Marinera by
OL,15,Fthe US.
OL,17,FPreviously known as the Bella-1, the
OL,18,FRussian-flagged vessel was captured by
OL,19,FAmerican forces aided by RAF aircraft
OL,20,Fand the British supply ship RFA
OL,21,FTideforce in the Atlantic.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FLater that same month, Royal Navy
OL,8,Fpatrol boat HMS Dagger helped the
OL,9,FFrench seize another sanctioned ship,
OL,10,Fthe Grinch, in the western
OL,11,FMediterranean, shadowing the vessel
OL,12,Fthrough the Strait of Gibraltar.
OL,14,FLast week, the French intercepted the
OL,15,FDeyna oil tanker in the Mediterranean,
OL,16,Fsupported by the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
