FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774534302
OL,3,CBritish forces will start seizing
OL,4,CRussian shadow fleet ships, PM
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FLibyan authorities have meanwhile
OL,8,Ftowed a suspected shadow fleet oil
OL,9,Ftanker found drifting in the
OL,10,FMediterranean which was believed to
OL,11,Fhave been hit in a drone strike.
OL,13,FThe tanker, carrying liquefied natural
OL,14,Fgas, was towed to avoid a spill in the
OL,15,FMediterranean.
OL,17,FAt the JEF summit, the Prime Minister
OL,18,Fand other leaders are expected to
OL,19,Fdiscuss shared security in the so-
OL,20,Fcalled High North and the war in
OL,21,FUkraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
